67
00:03:36,440 --> 00:03:37,280
Got it?

68
00:03:37,480 --> 00:03:38,320
Alright.

69
00:03:38,320 --> 00:03:39,280
Understood, Manager An.

70
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:40,280
