78
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:56,940
Are they still together?

79
00:04:02,760 --> 00:04:04,460
I'm sorry, Uncle Niu.

80
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:06,260
I've caused you trouble.

81
00:04:06,260 --> 00:04:07,360
(Organic Milk Farm)

82
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:08,560
It's such a small matter.

83
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:10,740
You could've just had Master Pi
to make a call.

84
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:14,020
My father…

85
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:16,700
passed away.

86
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:19,440
When…

87
00:04:19,880 --> 00:04:21,420
