88
00:04:24,960 --> 00:04:26,460
It's been a while.

89
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:32,040
Director, I just checked.

90
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:33,960
The batch of milk we delivered to Hua Su

91
00:04:33,960 --> 00:04:35,220
was without any issues.

92
00:04:35,360 --> 00:04:37,380
How can you prove
that there are no issues?

93
00:04:38,160 --> 00:04:39,380
Do you have the records?

94
00:04:40,280 --> 00:04:41,160
Please look here.

95
00:04:41,160 --> 00:04:42,800
The milk we supply to Hua Su

96
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:44,520
has always been from the same batch

97
00:04:44,520 --> 00:04:45,980
we use internally.

98
00:04:46,120 --> 00:04:47,560
All recent batches

99
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:48,600
are logged here.

100
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:49,780
You can verify them.

101
00:04:55,520 --> 00:04:56,420
This…

102
00:04:57,400 --> 00:04:58,580
this is your boyfriend?

103
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:00,980
No, no, no.

104
00:05:01,320 --> 00:05:02,160
Well,

105
00:05:02,480 --> 00:05:04,540
