106
00:05:06,280 --> 00:05:08,060
Forget it, it's not important.

107
00:05:09,320 --> 00:05:10,180
Director,

108
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:11,700
may I ask you a question?

109
00:05:11,880 --> 00:05:12,740
Go ahead.

110
00:05:15,640 --> 00:05:16,860
Do you recognize me?

111
00:05:19,080 --> 00:05:20,260
Sorry, I don't.

112
00:05:20,400 --> 00:05:21,540
Who are you?

113
00:05:23,160 --> 00:05:25,200
We all know you are the CEO.

114
00:05:25,200 --> 00:05:26,960
There's no need to mention it
to everyone.

115
00:05:26,960 --> 00:05:28,060
I wasn't asking you.

116
00:05:28,760 --> 00:05:29,600
Director,

117
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:31,300
what I meant was,

118
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:33,460
do I look familiar to you?

119
00:05:37,640 --> 00:05:38,840
Are you tired?

120
00:05:38,840 --> 00:05:41,340
Do you need a rest?

121
00:05:56,320 --> 00:05:57,480
Hello, Mr. Shu.

122
00:05:57,480 --> 00:05:59,380
You finally called back.

123
00:05:59,560 --> 00:06:00,640
Where on earth are you?

124
00:06:00,640 --> 00:06:02,080
Why didn't you reply to my messages?

125
00:06:02,080 --> 00:06:04,300
I'm worried about you.

126
00:06:04,960 --> 00:06:06,760
It's complicated.

127
00:06:06,760 --> 00:06:08,140
I'll tell you when I get back.

128
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:11,260
For now, check for me

129
00:06:11,520 --> 00:06:12,640
if I visited a milk farm

130
00:06:12,640 --> 00:06:14,300
or met a boss

131
00:06:14,440 --> 00:06:16,400
named Niu Yongtian before

132
00:06:16,400 --> 00:06:17,660
on my recent trips.

133
00:06:17,910 --> 00:06:18,760
Mr. Shu,

134
00:06:18,760 --> 00:06:20,500
I told you before.

135
00:06:20,760 --> 00:06:23,860
Yes, we have seen quite a few
milk-based foods

136
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:25,520
but have yet to visit

137
00:06:25,520 --> 00:06:27,100
any production sites.

138
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:29,420
And among the people you've met,

139
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:31,020
there's a no Mr. Niu.

140
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:33,980
So what's this all about?

141
00:06:34,840 --> 00:06:35,720
What about Fang Meng?

142
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:36,980
Are you still together?

143
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:38,260
Yes.

144
00:06:38,440 --> 00:06:39,920
We're still here.

145
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:41,380
Gao Ying, let me tell you something.

146
00:06:41,640 --> 00:06:43,680
I had a terrible day today.

147
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:45,860
I almost got arrested
for being mistaken as a thief.

148
00:06:46,320 --> 00:06:47,640
What were you doing?

149
00:06:47,640 --> 00:06:49,460
Weren't you investigating the milk farm?

150
00:06:50,200 --> 00:06:53,260
You'd better ask your Mr. Shu.

151
00:06:53,640 --> 00:06:56,340
Fortunately, I protected her in time,

152
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:57,620
or

153
00:06:57,880 --> 00:06:59,660
there will be irreversible consequences.

154
00:06:59,880 --> 00:07:01,920
How come your love story

155
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:04,580
suddenly turned into a drama?

156
00:07:05,200 --> 00:07:07,260
So what else did you do?

157
00:07:08,440 --> 00:07:10,220
You kissed Mr. Shu!

158
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:11,640
Yes.

159
00:07:12,120 --> 00:07:13,560
You all know

160
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:14,980
