161
00:07:15,640 --> 00:07:16,960
Yes, we know it.

162
00:07:16,960 --> 00:07:17,980
Then tell me,

163
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:21,040
after a guy kisses a girl,

164
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:23,060
