to apologize.

165
00:07:24,800 --> 00:07:26,820
Is he a jerk?

166
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:28,340
That was an accident.

167
00:07:29,280 --> 00:07:31,700
Fang Meng is genuinely fearless.

168
00:07:32,160 --> 00:07:34,180
Anything else?

169
00:07:35,440 --> 00:07:36,620
Don't overthink it.

170
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:38,540
I just acted on impulse.

171
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:41,180
I thought it'd make us even.

172
00:07:42,080 --> 00:07:43,500
I didn't think much of it.

173
00:07:45,600 --> 00:07:48,900
You're not falling for Mr. Shu, are you?

174
00:07:50,960 --> 00:07:52,120
You think so, too?

175
00:07:52,120 --> 00:07:54,660
You're Bo Fei Group's CEO,

176
00:07:54,840 --> 00:07:56,560
and are actively pursuing her.

177
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:57,940
How could she feel nothing?

178
00:08:01,520 --> 00:08:03,620
How could I possibly like him?

179
00:08:04,640 --> 00:08:05,980
I just don't understand

180
00:08:06,320 --> 00:08:08,160
why we keep

181
00:08:08,160 --> 00:08:10,700
getting tangled up like this.

182
00:08:11,160 --> 00:08:12,700
Do you know what this is?

183
00:08:13,240 --> 00:08:14,100
What?

184
00:08:14,680 --> 00:08:16,140
The law of attraction.

185
00:08:16,400 --> 00:08:17,800
Mr. Su and you

186
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:20,180
have an undeniable pull.

187
00:08:20,840 --> 00:08:23,380
Woman, you can't escape it.

188
00:08:32,240 --> 00:08:33,100
Fang Meng,

189
00:08:33,350 --> 00:08:35,320
you need to learn
to support yourself from now on.

190
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:36,360
If you need anything,

191
00:08:36,360 --> 00:08:37,600
just call me.

192
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:39,240
- Okay.
- These are local specialties

193
00:08:39,240 --> 00:08:40,480
we grew ourselves.

194
00:08:40,480 --> 00:08:41,760
Here, take them.

195
00:08:41,760 --> 00:08:42,980
Thank you.

196
00:08:43,120 --> 00:08:44,000
I'm leaving now.

197
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:45,220
- Drive safely.
- Bye-bye.

198
00:08:48,280 --> 00:08:49,540
I'm sorry, Mr. Shu.

199
00:08:49,720 --> 00:08:50,560
Take this.

200
00:09:16,650 --> 00:09:18,140
Wait, I'm not in the car yet, Mr. Shu.

201
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:49,940
Miss Shen.

202
00:09:50,640 --> 00:09:51,700
Brother Xie Jun.

203
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:53,180
I'm not at the hospital.

204
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:54,300
Is something the matter?

205
00:09:54,640 --> 00:09:55,980
It's nothing.

206
00:09:56,400 --> 00:09:59,460
I just wanted
to show you my new toy.

207
00:10:01,560 --> 00:10:02,780
I have work in the afternoon.

208
00:10:03,400 --> 00:10:04,300
Maybe next time.

209
00:10:05,120 --> 00:10:06,020
Wait, wait.

210
00:10:06,520 --> 00:10:08,060
- Brother Xie Jun.
- Miss Shen.

211
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:09,040
I really can't…

212
00:10:09,050 --> 00:10:09,900
Brother Xie Jun,

213
00:10:10,040 --> 00:10:11,300
are you at the lakeside

214
00:10:11,560 --> 00:10:12,860
wearing black?

215
00:10:23,520 --> 00:10:24,560
How do you know?

216
00:10:24,560 --> 00:10:27,460
Turn around, look back.

217
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:30,660
Brother Xie Jun.

218
00:10:30,880 --> 00:10:34,520
Today, I'm invincible Sailor Shen An'an,

219
00:10:34,520 --> 00:10:37,500
coming riding the waves for you!

220
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:39,440
Brother Xie Jun,

221
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:42,300
do you like it?

222
00:10:49,040 --> 00:10:49,880
Go!

223
00:10:49,880 --> 00:10:52,120
Brother Xie Jun, don't run!

224
00:10:52,120 --> 00:10:54,060
Where are you going, Brother Xie Jun?

225
00:10:55,160 --> 00:10:57,020
Guys, go!

226
00:11:01,280 --> 00:11:02,520
Don't run!

227
00:11:02,520 --> 00:11:03,860
Why are you avoiding me?

228
00:11:04,420 --> 00:11:09,060
(Hua Su)

229
00:11:09,800 --> 00:11:13,260
No. 12 trial
of Calm Milk Volcano Noodles,

230
00:11:13,720 --> 00:11:14,560
begin!

231
00:11:21,880 --> 00:11:22,720
Hey!

232
00:11:24,480 --> 00:11:25,800
Didn't I already tell you?

233
00:11:25,800 --> 00:11:27,300
Stay out of my kitchen!

234
00:11:27,640 --> 00:11:28,980
I just want to learn.

235
00:11:29,920 --> 00:11:30,840
Learn what?

236
00:11:30,840 --> 00:11:32,260
I don't even know how to do it yet!

237
00:11:33,040 --> 00:11:34,500
Then who taught you?

238
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:35,900
My Dad.

239
00:11:36,480 --> 00:11:39,620
Was his cooking just as bad as yours?

240
00:11:40,590 --> 00:11:42,060
♪Getting closer and closer♪

241
00:11:42,400 --> 00:11:44,140
He's not like me.

242
00:11:45,320 --> 00:11:47,980
He was a fantastic chef.

243
00:11:49,560 --> 00:11:50,940
Since you have no taste,

244
00:11:51,400 --> 00:11:53,140
why not just follow the recipe?

245
00:11:53,400 --> 00:11:55,200
Just take a look at his recipe.

246
00:11:55,200 --> 00:11:56,920
It's a total mess!

247
00:11:56,920 --> 00:11:58,330
Probably only he could make sense of it.

248
00:11:58,340 --> 00:11:59,590
♪I will be careful even when I'm sad♪

249
00:11:59,600 --> 00:12:01,550
♪Treat you as a sensitive topic♪

250
00:12:01,550 --> 00:12:04,580
♪Who knows when the clear sky
suddenly brings rain around us♪

251
00:12:04,960 --> 00:12:06,540
Meng, Fang Meng.

252
00:12:07,240 --> 00:12:08,120
Look.

253
00:12:08,120 --> 00:12:09,380
This is not our bucket.

254
00:12:10,920 --> 00:12:11,920
Our buckets

255
00:12:11,920 --> 00:12:13,920
always have dated labels,

256
00:12:13,920 --> 00:12:15,200
but this one doesn't.

257
00:12:15,200 --> 00:12:17,000
I clearly remember that

258
00:12:17,000 --> 00:12:18,460
I personally attached the label.

259
00:12:18,920 --> 00:12:20,500
This isn't ours.

260
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:23,820
Someone swapped our milk.

261
00:12:24,240 --> 00:12:25,460
Who would do that?

262
00:12:28,760 --> 00:12:30,280
If Hua Su fails,

263
00:12:30,280 --> 00:12:31,300
who would benefit from it?

264
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:35,440
Besides Bo Fei Group…

265
00:12:35,440 --> 00:12:37,180
Why exclude the Bo Fei Group?

266
00:12:38,720 --> 00:12:40,700
We wouldn't use such malicious methods.

267
00:12:43,200 --> 00:12:44,780
Could it be An Zhijiang?

268
00:12:46,400 --> 00:12:47,240
Impossible.

269
00:12:47,920 --> 00:12:48,760
If it were him,

270
00:12:48,760 --> 00:12:49,840
this would only help me.

271
00:12:49,840 --> 00:12:50,680
He won't do this.

272
00:12:58,840 --> 00:12:59,820
I understand now.

273
00:13:01,920 --> 00:13:03,440
Before acquiring Hua Su,

274
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:04,880
Bo Fei Group will only sign

275
00:13:04,880 --> 00:13:06,360
intention agreements
with other vendors.

276
00:13:06,360 --> 00:13:08,240
They only receive a deposit,

277
00:13:08,240 --> 00:13:10,280
but not the full payment

278
00:13:10,280 --> 00:13:12,620
until Food Street is settled

279
00:13:14,040 --> 00:13:16,360
and the formal acquisition agreements
are signed.

280
00:13:16,360 --> 00:13:18,500
Hua Su is their biggest obstacle.

281
00:13:21,640 --> 00:13:24,100
They of all parties
should want Hua Su closed.

282
00:13:26,040 --> 00:13:27,380
Is there any solution?

283
00:13:30,360 --> 00:13:31,200
Of course there is.

284
00:13:31,960 --> 00:13:32,800
Say it.

285
00:13:33,160 --> 00:13:34,740
Sell Hua Su to Bo Fei Group,

286
00:13:34,880 --> 00:13:36,500
and all problems will be solved.

287
00:13:37,600 --> 00:13:38,440
Wait a moment.

288
00:13:41,160 --> 00:13:43,940
There's another way.

